# Intro Demo

Output examples/svgs/branding/intro.svg

Set FontSize 16
Set Template macos
Set Theme verminal
Set LoopStyle fade
Set Background "gradient(hotpink, #8A00C4:horizontal)"
Set BackgroundPadding 25
Set CursorStyle bar
Set WorkingDirectory "examples/cds/branding"

Type "cat welcome.txt | lolcat -f"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Type "Welcome to DVD!" 
Sleep 1s
Space
Type "Create cool SVG animations from .cd files or piped input 🤯"
Sleep 1s
